				\begin{document}$$\:{\mathrm{X}}_{\mathrm{drop}}=\mathrm{Dropout}\left({\mathrm{X}}_{\mathrm{dense}},\mathrm{p}=0.5\right)$$\end{document}

This output feeds into another dense layer:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
